title: [Gingie's General Store]
[Gingie's Armory]
[Gingie's Outfitting]
description: Enclosed by celadon marble walls, the shop features a handblown double-heart bottle in the center of its black marble floor.  A blue watered silk tapestry hangs under the vaulted ceiling.  Right near the front is a gold-leafed mistwood cabinet and an etched brass bin.
